=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de554a733cf01e22e0757fbaf10dc6f8d297ba6","tid":1564054,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n@希望連仔幫手壓制fake news <br />\n@上連登要用多用腦！<br />\n最新活動：唱民主聖歌，傳福音！<br />\n杯葛商場：齋睇唔買，儲多d錢！<br />\n913中秋賞燈晚會，連儂牆見！<br />\n連儂牆戰線不能倒！修建連儂，有你有我<br />\n<ins>考驗毅力與堅持</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n#離開同溫層，接觸各種人，理解佢地嘅想法，將不支持我們的人轉為支持我們！這是成功的方法！<br />\n<br />\n@Template@<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</span><br />\n<em>每日任務：</em><br />\n1. 優先<span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心商店<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n3. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點咆哮</span>！（改9點會少好多人）<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">健身+運動</span>，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmCUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=50f33281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會，陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.12 @Template End@"},{"pid":"c831b4d62e2cbe74a79fbb9b8126da450003d3d9","tid":1564054,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"我 地 輸 在 行 動 力 細 ，大 家 太 睇 少 自 己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1564004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1564004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05c2aea1c51b60301a5e9bb5ab5a9c283961c79c","tid":1564054,"uid":110878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"一係就一日十幾萬個post重現雨革，一係就十幾萬個post屌鳩勇武。 指人點樣點樣，又唔見用依d時間開d行動post 屌你老母"},{"pid":"7e95c82b4a6662cf6ff14d9a39db9f26a2b99f01","tid":1564054,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c2aea1c51b60301a5e9bb5ab5a9c283961c79c","tid":1564054,"uid":110878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"一係就一日十幾萬個post重現雨革，一係就十幾萬個post屌鳩勇武。 指人點樣點樣，又唔見用依d時間開d行動post 屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:38:00.000Z","msg":"有行動就一晚幾十萬個Post求人走 留返x.xx"},{"pid":"53cccfc17fa65c98624a8719172253928b9b7f1d","tid":1564054,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你估冷氣軍師流㗎"},{"pid":"005479f9e45a5f75aa13b60d5051bea47e2d1137","tid":1564054,"uid":10812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"屌真喎<br />\n又話前線自決<br />\n又話抗爭唔一定要苦行式<br />\n結果每晚都有啲屌手足既post<br />\n講真係現場無論氣氛定情況<br />\n都無連登軍師形容到咁差咁惡劣<br />\n不分化不篤灰<br />\n我唔鐘意搞連儂牆<br />\n但係我會幫手哨<br />\n我唔鐘意玩陣地戰<br />\n但係我會齊上齊落<br />\n有咩意見可以提出黎<br />\n不完美 但可改進<br />\n唔係一味插屌批鬥<br />\n希望大家真係諗諗"},{"pid":"29dd5cc44e2f1c2c786b68cb4a169537f0e9dd06","tid":1564054,"uid":2142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"果堆分化撚黎架啫<br />\n唔撚使理佢地<br 